Your areas of responsibility will include both Projects & BAU in a LINUX
environment and technologies include:  

  * \- CI/CD & data services, & most other applicable software and infrastructure 
  * \- Cloud Infrastructure 
    * \- AWS cloud environment 
    * \- Migration of most services running in AWS (with ECS/EC2) to Kubernetes (EKS) 
    * \- Automation & Scripting (Bash, Python, Powershell) 
    * \- IAC (CloudFormation, ARM, AWS CDK, Terraform & Ansible) 
  
Required Skills:  
